Namespace nORM.SourceGeneration

Classes

CompileTimeQueryAttribute

Indicates that a method should be populated by the source generator with a pre-compiled query using the provided SQL statement.

CompiledMaterializerStore

GenerateMaterializerAttribute

Marks an entity type for which a materializer should be generated at compile time. The associated source generator will produce a method that can populate an instance of the decorated type directly from a DbDataReader.
